{"tid":1094668,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"戶田惠梨香劣化！晨間劇《緋紅》15歲少女青春扮相曝光 網友負評連連「好像是懲罰遊戲」","createTime":"2019-04-06T12:55:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-06T18:11:51.000Z","uid":9573,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"25e8d87264cd686d275463a3da833a499de031c4","tid":1094668,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T12:55:41.000Z","msg":"日本女星戶田惠梨香13年前憑著在電影《死亡筆記本》飾演「彌海砂」一角爆紅，綁著雙馬尾的超萌扮相奠定她女神地位。然而現年30歲的她，日前為主演晨間劇《緋紅》宣傳，還曝光了劇中15歲少女扮相，只是網友負評連連，驚呼好像是懲罰遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190405/photo/bkn-20190405121152503-0405_00862_001_02b.jpg?20190405181046\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190405%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190405121152503-0405_00862_001_02b.jpg%3F20190405181046&h=6fc90ee0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本女星戶田惠梨香去年主演的催淚愛情劇《大戀愛》獲好評後，火速接拍NHK電視台第101部晨早劇《Scarlet》，將於今年9月首播，並於4月在滋賀縣甲賀市開鏡。已踏入30歲的戶田在劇飾演陶藝家川原喜美子，由少女時代15歲演到50幾歲中年，故事背景橫跨戰後50、60年代的日本經濟起飛到泡沬爆破，相當具挑戰性。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2019-04-06/900/20190406002319.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2019-04-06%2F900%2F20190406002319.jpg&h=d4d8b63a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n戶田惠梨香18歲演出彌海砂一角。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2019-04-06/900/20190406002315.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2019-04-06%2F900%2F20190406002315.jpg&h=8377a375&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n戶田惠梨香扮15歲少女，日網友驚嚇不已。<br />\n<br />\n她與拍檔大島優子現身滋賀拍攝，而在劇中的15歲造型首次曝光。後衛謝路美保定盛傳今夏會被拜仁慕尼黑清洗，竟然在今晚德甲榜首大戰鬥多蒙特前，為傾力宣傳還特地穿上水手服，不過日本網友對於她的少女扮相吐槽不斷，「像大媽一樣了呢」、「即使不是顯老的人，也看得出時間的殘酷呢」、「大媽在玩cosplay」，感嘆當年那個風靡萬千少男心「彌海砂」真的回不去了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190405/photo/bkn-20190405121152503-0405_00862_001_05b.jpg?20190405181046\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190405%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190405121152503-0405_00862_001_05b.jpg%3F20190405181046&h=5ed13997&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190405/photo/bkn-20190405121152503-0405_00862_001_06b.jpg?20190405181046\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190405%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190405121152503-0405_00862_001_06b.jpg%3F20190405181046&h=06cf90bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，自去年與成田凌分手後，戶田不愁寂寞，新一期雜誌《Friday》拍到她駕車到目黑區，相約兩名男友人在高級壽司店晚飯，期間與友人睇手機哈哈大笑。"},{"pid":"cba8f6bf576063d7e67b46642f7bc80fe529e6a9","tid":1094668,"uid":189269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T13:10:05.000Z","msg":"咁就13年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c047315e4dbc91988ba357284ad92711e2f17542","tid":1094668,"uid":152123,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T13:11:53.000Z","msg":"由少女時代15歲演到50幾歲中年<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又唔係淨演15 咪撚煩啦"},{"pid":"a20b2d809ae69c35db08c78518a65c21ad7c2c14","tid":1094668,"uid":54959,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T14:37:33.000Z","msg":"後衛謝路美保定盛傳今夏會被拜仁慕尼黑清洗，竟然在今晚德甲榜首大戰鬥多蒙特前，為傾力宣傳還特地穿上水手服，<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"777e38239d893ea218b9ab70b99ba01a1c9db3df","tid":1094668,"uid":81273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T14:39:27.000Z","msg":"大島傻子有工開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1d092650d267cf40d5d8e8ae157fb4010699a86","tid":1094668,"uid":9104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a20b2d809ae69c35db08c78518a65c21ad7c2c14","tid":1094668,"uid":54959,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T14:37:33.000Z","msg":"後衛謝路美保定盛傳今夏會被拜仁慕尼黑清洗，竟然在今晚德甲榜首大戰鬥多蒙特前，為傾力宣傳還特地穿上水手服，<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/f